  m_text: "The video call blinks to life \u2014 Boyet waves, books scattered all
    over his desk. \u201CKaya natin \u2018to,\u201D he laughs as they quiz each other
    on formulas and notes. The night grows late, but the mood stays light. Between
    yawns and laughter, Alex feels it \u2014 maybe college won\u2019t be so scary
    after all"
