  chapter1DialogueIntro:
  - speaker: Alex
    text: "I\u2019m finally in college, can\u2019t wait to start my first day! "
  - speaker: Alex
    text: "I\u2019m so excited to make new friends along the way and create some
      unforgettable memories."
  - speaker: Alex
    text: "But first, Ma & Pa just gave me my allowance. I\u2019m getting hungry
      and I should start thinking about how I\u2019m going to budget all this money
      that I currently have."
  chapter1DialogueBoyet:
  - speaker: Alex
    text: "My name\u2019s Alex by the way, what\u2019s your name?"
  - speaker: 
    text: Nice to meet you Alex! My name is Boyet!
  - speaker: Alex
    text: Nice to meet you too, Boyet! Anyways, I have to go now, my parents would
      want to know how my first day went. We should go and hangout sometime soon!
  - speaker: Boyet
    text: We definitely have to, for sure! See you tomorrow then, Alex!
  chapter2Dialogue:
  - speaker: Alex
    text: Hoy Boyet, ready ka na ba sa exam mamaya?
  - speaker: Boyet
    text: Hindi pa nga eh. Kinakabahan ako
  - speaker: Alex
    text: Same. Pero laban lang
  - speaker: Alex
    text: Sandali lang. May aasikasuhin muna ako
  finalChapter2Dialogue:
  - speaker: alex
    text: Ang haba pala ng araw pag college na
  - speaker: alex
    text: Kailangan ko talagang alagaan sarili ko
