      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The morning sun filters through the window as Alex rushes into class,
    half-awake and clutching a cup of coffee. The lecture drones on \u2014 and before
    long, eyelids get heavy. A quick head nod, then\u2014oops\u2014caught by the
    professor. Laughter ripples through the room.\r\n\r\nBy lunchtime, the mood lightens.
    Alex joins Boyet and the others, trading jokes over rice meals and soda. Stories,
    laughter, and plans for group projects fill the air. As the day ends, Alex heads
    home \u2014 notebooks heavier, heart a little fuller. Another normal day, another
    small victory"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
